  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">At 10th level the words of the flagellant know how to guide the multitudes. If you have less than half your maximum hit points, you can use Irresistible Speech on all targets within 60 feet or on a unit under your command. As long as creatures are charmed in this way, they can re-roll the first saving throw they fail.</span> </p>",
